An example program of using OpenGL with Gtk4. You can see different moving figures, change number of filgures in the window, stop and start moving.

To build:
cmake -S moving_figures -B /tmp/moving_figures/release -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=GlibToolChain.cmake

To install:
cmake --build /tmp/moving_figures/release --config Release --target install DESTDIR=$HOME/.local
